name: Don Kiki - Black Label - Toro
additionalNotes: Don KiKi Black Label all NEW blend by Estelí Cigar Factory S.A. with exceptional full body taste.  A full body cigar with a clean and smooth draw crafted in an old style pigtail, that gives you hints of leather and the sweetness of the wrapper comes through the entire cigar which reminds you of a classic vintage maduro. The filler and binder are Puro Esteliano.
